  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为技能注册表设计一个状态流转图。核心场景是：用户从Education_ContentCDN获取内容后，先进入idle状态，然后通过SCAN操作进入scanned状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "idle",
        "scanned",
        "SCAN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，idle是初始状态。那scanned之后用户可以做什么？是直接进入viewing查看详情，还是有其他分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned",
        "viewing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，scanned之后用SELECT进入viewing。这里有个细节：在scanned状态可以重复SCAN来刷新列表，所以scanned要有自环。另外viewing也能SELECT，比如连续查看多个技能详情。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned",
        "viewing",
        "SELECT",
        "scanned自环",
        "viewing自环"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：idle→scanned→viewing，加上scanned和viewing的自环。那从viewing能返回scanned吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "scanned",
        "viewing",
        "BACK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，用BACK操作返回scanned。还有EXPORT功能，scanned和viewing状态都要支持导出。最后加个RESET从scanned回到idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BACK",
        "EXPORT",
        "RESET",
        "idle",
        "scanned",
        "viewing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "检查一遍：scanned有两个自环（SCAN刷新和EXPORT导出），viewing也有两个自环（SELECT连续查看和EXPORT导出）。BACK从viewing到scanned，RESET从scanned回idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "scanned自环",
        "viewing自环",
        "BACK",
        "RESET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚注意到Education_ContentCDN应该是起点，不是状态节点。它应该用方括号表示，然后直接指向idle，不需要触发条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，Education_ContentCDN作为外部实体用方括号标注，无触发条件直接连接到idle。整个stateDiagram-v2结构现在完整了。",
